'''查爾斯·赫希·貝瑞'''（{{lang-en|Charles Hirsch Barris}}，{{bd|1929年|6月26日|2017年|3月21日}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/chuck-barris-dead-dies-gong-show-host-1202013790/|title=Chuck Barris, 'Gong Show' Host, Dies at 87|first=Pat|last=Saperstein|work=Variety|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322075334/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/chuck-barris-dead-dies-gong-show-host-1202013790/|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一名美國[[遊戲節目|遊戲節目]]創作者、製片人、主持人、詞曲作家和作家。他以主持《{{le|銅鑼秀|The Gong Show}}》和創作《{{le|約會遊戲|The Dating Game}}》和《{{le|新婚遊戲|The Newlywed Game}}》而聞名。他還寫了{{le|弗雷迪·卡農|Freddy Cannon}}演唱的〈{{le|帕利塞茲公園 (弗雷迪·卡農歌曲)|Palisades Park (Freddy Cannon song)|帕利塞茲公園}}〉一曲。

貝瑞還知名於撰寫的自傳《危險心靈的自白》（{{lang|en|''Confessions of a Dangerous Mind''}}），內容講述自己電視事業和心路歷程之餘，亦加入了自己曾在[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]工作的秘密，但書出版後的1984年，他承認中央情報局的經歷實屬捏造。該書於2002年改編成電影《[[神經殺手|神經殺手]]》，由[[喬治·克隆尼|喬治·克隆尼]]執導，[[山姆·洛克威爾|山姆·洛克威爾]]飾演貝瑞。<ref name="BuzzerBlog(2017-03-22)">{{cite news|url=http://buzzerblog.com/2017/03/22/rip-chuck-barris/|title=RIP Chuck Barris|last=Carrion|first=Christian|work=BuzzerBlog|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2021-01-31|quote=in a 1984 interview on NBC's Today show, he once put the rumors to rest: "No, I was never a CIA hit man. I never did those things. I once applied for the CIA, and while I was going through the process I got a job and went on television. But I had always wondered what would have happened if I had done both."|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128124606/http://buzzerblog.com/2017/03/22/rip-chuck-barris/|archive-date=2021-01-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

